description: The Plugable "SuperSpeed" USB 3.0 6:1 Multi Card Reader is a fast, durable, multipurpose data reading machine!Featuring support for most modern media cards makes this a great choice for digital media enthusiasts with a variety of devices and card types.  Have a USB 3.0 capable PC and an older USB 2.0 media card reader?  USB 3.0 "SuperSpeed" card readers can more than double your real world data transfer speeds, cutting the time to access your media in half.  Includes a LED to indicate whether the device is powered (steady light) or currently transferring data (flashing light), so you can tell whether your transfers have completed with a glance across the room.Small enough for a laptop or tablet case, with no power supply and only a USB 3.0 cable to connect the device, this is a great option for on-the-go digital photo enthusiasts. Anyone who wants to quickly copy pictures to their notebook or tablet and get back to shooting will love this card reader!Uses Genesys Logic GL3220 chipset featuring*Supported card types include: CF, SD, SDXC, SDHC, MicroSD, XD, MemoryStick, MMC, M2*CompactFlash UDMA 7 cards are supported in UDMA 6 mode up to 133 MB/sec*SD, SDHC, and SDXC cards are supported in UHS-I mode up to 104 MB/secCompatibility*Supports Windows 8/8.1, 7, Vista, XP*Mac OS 9 and above*Linux: Modern kernel 2.x & 3.x based distributions with USB Mass storage supportIn the Box1 Card reader1 USB 3.0 A to USB 3.0 Micro B cable1 User Manual
title: Plugable Aluminum SuperSpeed USB 3.0 12-in-1 6 slot Memory Card Reader (Including UDMA CF and UHS-I SD, SDXC, SDHC, MicroSD)
